headline: ‘Blue Sky’ Reaches New Altitude: JetBlue and United Begin Offering Sales Across Both Airlines
summary: NEW YORK & CHICAGO, February 10, 2026--JetBlue (Nasdaq: JBLU) and United Airlines (Nasdaq: UAL) today announced the roll out of the next major customer benefit from their Blue Sky collaboration: beginning this week, travelers can start to purchase eligible itineraries operated by either airline directly on JetBlue.com, United.com and each airline’s mobile app.
